TopicTitle: Proton/Soyuz space adventures style lunar fly by mission.

Articles.Content: Does anyone know how to preform a Mun fly by with a proton rocket with a munar fly by stage as well as some sorta Soyuz mod? I prefer stock alike solar system mods for these vehicles.
I have made a stock Soyuz by using the Making History stuff. I suppose it can have just enough fuel for a munar fly-by. Maybe even the Vostok?
